    "title": "Hiring Medical Officer at Hinduja Healthcare Digital Technologies",
    "description": "We at Hinduja Healthcare Digital Technologies are looking for an experienced Medical Officer based out of Jodhpur. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Hinduja Healthcare Digital Technologies:\nHinduja Healthcare Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Referral bonus program\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Hinduja Healthcare Digital Technologies!",
